	<h1 class="title">Nike 首发欧文战靴，不过把发布会开到了篮球游戏里</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/103970/small/103970.jpg?1431972719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">朱凯麟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-14 14:38:32 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19029/medium/19029.jpg?1450071673" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


